<% title "Sensei - Home" %>
<section class="cover height-70 imagebg parallax" data-overlay="6">
  <div class="background-image-holder">
    <%= image_tag "background/home.jpg" %>
  </div>
  <div class="container pos-vertical-center">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-9 col-md-12 mt--3">
        <h1 class="">
          Learn Anything from Amazing Teachers
        </h1>
        <!-- <p class="lead">
        </p> -->
        <a class="btn btn--primary type--uppercase inner-link" href="#about">
          <span class="btn__text">
            How it works
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="unpad">
  <div class="row--gapless">
    <%= render "categories" %>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <div class="">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="masonry__container">
              <%= render 'shared/list', lessons: @lessons %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="about" class="text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-10 col-md-8">
        <h2>About Studiate</h2>
        <p class="lead">
         We at Studiate believe that it is important that you keep learning throughout your live and that the things you learn define you as a person. But we also understand that it is sometimes difficult do get started because you don't now where to begin. Would you agree that it would nice if you had someone to help you get started? Someone like a teacher?
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
          Studiate gives everyone the possibiltiy to learn with the help of a amazing teacher. At Studiate you can find and book a skilled teacher near you.
          You make an account and search by category for a teacher. When you found a teacher you like, you make an appointment and the teacher will automatically receive your booking. After receiving the booking, the teacher will contact you using your personal information in your profile. It is that simple!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!--end of row-->
  </div>
  <!--end of container-->
</section>

